name: Orbe
description:
Introduction

Short and flat canyon with high water flow, with several jump possibilities and a crazy amount of natural arches. Be cautious, big dams are above the canyon. If you want to do an Abseil as well, walk higher up to the Saut du Day, a 20m wide slab waterfall.
